## Travel scholarships

Depending on our level of sponsorship, we should be able to fund a few "travel scholarships" in the form of paid-for accommodation in Oxford and/or transportation. We hope to be able to confirm this by the end of March 2025. If you are a student and would benefit from this support, please send an application letter to [Wouter Mostert](/sandbox/wmostert/README).

